{"tid":1054771,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"飛機空中失事絕望 定係潛艇出事絕望？","createTime":"2019-03-10T05:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T07:12:41.000Z","uid":14075,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"81a3fc33443ef701012946dff69775a49bb2ccad","tid":1054771,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"空難可以睇隔離post<br />\n潛艇出事好似俄羅斯最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115d72781852f6705ca9eb251eda0d4c9c913cbf","tid":1054771,"uid":159876,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:36:25.000Z","msg":"飛機失事跌落海，變潛艇最絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386edcdbf2ed35d9ed70e5913457b0b5fe297540","tid":1054771,"uid":35129,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:36:47.000Z","msg":"自己一個玩降落傘連後備都開唔到絕望啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a148b724b8399f75ba1b45090c0fcd688311144","tid":1054771,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"115d72781852f6705ca9eb251eda0d4c9c913cbf","tid":1054771,"uid":159876,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:36:25.000Z","msg":"飛機失事跌落海，變潛艇最絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:39:38.000Z","msg":"水中解體應該都係水面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe0fda0a1131959a429450e02735bf053d203fd","tid":1054771,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"橫死掂死，緊係死快d好喇"},{"pid":"63669d800b8c6966720b3b9d3f38be3e75779328","tid":1054771,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbe0fda0a1131959a429450e02735bf053d203fd","tid":1054771,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"橫死掂死，緊係死快d好喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"浸死算唔算快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4cbcde4cc843b01e5ebbbc5ff156ba134ef09f","tid":1054771,"uid":14075,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"庫爾斯克號沉到108公尺深的海底，沉沒點離北莫爾斯克約135公里，地理位置是北緯69&deg;40'，東經37&deg;35'。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">庫爾斯克號未能放出求救浮標，且用聲納或磁探均難以探測，為定位即消耗了最初的數十小時</span>。雖然俄羅斯和挪威試圖營救，但艇內水手和軍官仍全部死亡。後來的研究發現艇內大多數人死於爆炸後數分鐘內。但第6區段及其後的23人聚集至最後的第9區段，還倖存了數十小時（沉沒的船頭接觸海底，船尾懸浮在水中，斜向海面；船員打開隔艙門匯合後，各艙均進水，殘存的空氣匯聚至船尾，在第9區段形成一個不大的壓縮氣室）；後因黑暗中不慎將氧氣再生板掉落積水中，並引發火災耗盡船尾氧氣，所有船員不幸遇難。"},{"pid":"e6c4ba817479fea7e92f9aea68742b035ed5cc7e","tid":1054771,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:50:38.000Z","msg":"潛艇如果知道位置其實救唔救到"},{"pid":"59f5b3cba6011e02644ad535e900c5289606bd40","tid":1054771,"uid":220368,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"潛艇，浸死要時間，好絕望<br />\n飛機失事爆炸死都係一𣊬間，好彩嘅遇到天才機師滑行海面可能唔洗死添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf873cf47b5a378c4d4646dbe50253854386dec","tid":1054771,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63669d800b8c6966720b3b9d3f38be3e75779328","tid":1054771,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbe0fda0a1131959a429450e02735bf053d203fd","tid":1054771,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"橫死掂死，緊係死快d好喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"浸死算唔算快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:59:38.000Z","msg":"但未浸死前，d水可能係慢慢流2日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b5b29afc0d9ebaa2e7ec6f13f2e90c7a0a8ac8","tid":1054771,"uid":52942,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"飛機失事都可以左腳踏右腳慢慢落跳上天，或者臨落地個一下跳一跳唔使死，但係潛水艇真係無得救，你睇年中幾多連登仔潛水一潛就無再浦過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dcab27303c98cc94d8e84ed3748f43acf7b0e2","tid":1054771,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71b5b29afc0d9ebaa2e7ec6f13f2e90c7a0a8ac8","tid":1054771,"uid":52942,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"飛機失事都可以左腳踏右腳慢慢落跳上天，或者臨落地個一下跳一跳唔使死，但係潛水艇真係無得救，你睇年中幾多連登仔潛水一潛就無再浦過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:08:35.000Z","msg":"快速上水身體細胞好似會頂唔到"},{"pid":"0b909ef290c97cd98b18772fcfa999b5c2e35bed","tid":1054771,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"無錢絕望d"},{"pid":"5d5d74ae5a342289255c3c57c674b3e44d653b96","tid":1054771,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e6c4ba817479fea7e92f9aea68742b035ed5cc7e","tid":1054771,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:50:38.000Z","msg":"潛艇如果知道位置其實救唔救到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"美帝以前冷戰果時打撈左隻蘇聯沉左但係唔夠技術打撈既潛艇上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a79be88b172b7af88ff080afa23ab46246645cc","tid":1054771,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"潛艇，慢慢等死先最恐怖"},{"pid":"a5e9f07a905f875c53b52620f30303c715132ecf","tid":1054771,"uid":32713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b909ef290c97cd98b18772fcfa999b5c2e35bed","tid":1054771,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"無錢絕望d"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"